    'HsCode',
    'Harmonized System chapter reference. 17 HS chapters in CargoIntelligence. Flags is_tobacco_chapter (ch.24) and is_disguise_category (ch.20,22,25,39,63,94). Chapters 20,22,24,25,39,63,94 have benchmark value_per_kg from UN Comtrade TradeStats.',
